Package cz.cuni.mff.d3s.trupple.language.runtime.customvalues

Package containing runtime representations of variables of Pascal-specific types.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FileValue
    Interface for representations of variables of file types.
    PascalArray
    Interface for all array-type variables.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EnumValue
    Represents Pascal enum-type variable.
    ObjectFileValue
    Representation of a file type value of generic inner type.
    PascalString
    Representation of a string-type variable.
    PascalSubroutine
    Representation of a subroutine-type variable.
    PCharValue
    Representation of variables of PChar type.
    PointerValue
    Representation of pointer type variables.
    RecordValue
    Representation of record-type variables.
    Reference
    Representation of variables passed as a reference to subroutines.
    SetTypeValue
    Representation of set-type variables.
    TextFileValue
    Representation of textfile-type variables.

Package cz.cuni.mff.d3s.trupple.language.runtime.customvalues Description

Package containing runtime representations of variables of Pascal-specific types. Objects of these classes are stored inside frames.
